                                      throws java.lang.ClassNotFoundException,

        Deprecated.

        Register all commands in a specific package
        Parameters:
        server - The bukkit server
        pkg - The package path (e.g. com.ristexsoftware.knappy.commands)
        Returns:
        False if something went horribly wrong
        Throws:
        java.lang.ClassNotFoundException - If the comamnd class cannot be located
        java.lang.IllegalAccessException - if the command class represents an abstract class, an interface, an array class, a primitive type, or void; or if the class has no nullary constructor; or if the instantiation fails for some other reason.
